    v2 = 1.0

    tmp = (0.31 / 0.99)
    v2 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.44 + v2 + 0.60)) * wp.sin(0.80))
    v2 = (0.57 / (0.23 + wp.abs(tmp + 1.00)))
    v2 = 0.64
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((v1 + 0.36 * v0 + 0.42)))
